        "options": [
          "A. √9",
          "B. 0.75",
          "C. -4/5",
          "D. √2"
        ],
        "answer": "D. √2",
        "explanation": "√9 simplifies to 3 (rational), 0.75 is a terminating decimal (rational), and -4/5 is a fraction (rational). √2 has a non-terminating, non-repeating decimal expansion.",
