          "B. Integers and Fractions",
          "C. Rational Numbers and Irrational Numbers",
          "D. Positive and Negative Numbers"
        ],
        "answer": "C. Rational Numbers and Irrational Numbers",
        "explanation": "Real numbers encompass all rational numbers (terminating or repeating decimals) and irrational numbers (non-terminating, non-repeating decimals).",
        "marks": 1,
        "learningOutcomeIds": [
          "LO1"
